s Lab</a>&nbsp;to register for this pop-up.</span></p>\n\n<p><em>Photo from UCSF staff member Brenda</em></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><strong>Have questions about the Makers Lab?</strong> Visit the <a href=\"https://www.library.ucsf.edu/use/makerslab/\" target=\"_self\">Makers Lab webpage</a> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">or <a href=\"https://www.library.ucsf.edu/ask-an-expert/makers-lab-support/\" target=\"_self\">contact us</a></span></span></span>. <span style=\"font-size:14px;\">The Makers Lab is open by appointment for UCSF teaching, learning, and research projects. Contact the <a href=\"https://www.library.ucsf.edu/ask-an-expert/makers-lab-support/\">Makers Lab</a> to schedule an appointment. </span></span></span></p>","url":{"public":"https://calendars.library.ucsf.edu/event/15918953","admin":"https://calendars.library.ucsf.edu/aevent.php?c=928&m=edit&event_id=15918953"},"location":"","campus":"Online","category":[{"id":25201,"name":"Makers Lab"},{"id":57276,"name":"Needlecraft"}],"owner":{"id":16958,"name":"UCSF Library Makers Lab"},"presenter":"Ariel Deardorff","calendar":{"id":928,"name":"Library Events and Classes","public":"https://calendars.library.ucsf.edu/calendar/events","admin":"https://calendars.library.ucsf.edu/admin/calendar/928"},"seats":12,"registration":true,"registration_form_id":16241,"registration_series_linked":false,"has_registration_opened":true,"registration_open_at":"2025-12-05T13:17:20-08:00","has_registration_closed":false,"registration_close_at":"2026-07-10T12:00:00-07:00","physical_seats":0,"physical_seats_taken":0,"online_seats":12,"online_seats_taken":4,"seats_taken":4,"wait_list":true,"color":"#EB093C","featured_image":"https://d68g328n4ug0e.cloudfront.net/data/feat_img/138/928/1764969430.jpg","featured_image_alt_text":"","geolocation